  "appPurposeHeroTitle": "Conscious Spending,\nFree Future.",
  "appPurposeHeroDesc": "Pretio transforms your expenses from mere numbers into their true impact on your life, helping you replace impulsive urges with conscious decisions that lead you to your dreams.",
  "feature1Title": "Fast and Practical Logging",
  "feature1Desc": "Log your expenses instantly and effortlessly. Instead of tedious forms, add your transactions in seconds, turning financial tracking into a pleasant daily habit.",
  "feature2Title": "Emotional Finance Compass",
  "feature2Desc": "Discover the psychology behind every expense. Is it a real need or a sudden urge? Map your consumption habits and allocate your money only to things that bring you value.",
  "feature3Title": "Focus on Your Dreams",
  "feature3Desc": "Plan not just for today, but for the future. Clearly see how close you are to your dream goal and direct your savings straight towards it.",
  "feature4Title": "Detailed Analytics and Habit Tracking",
  "feature4Desc": "See transparently where your money goes. Discover your consumption habits by examining your spending trends and emotional distribution in detail with elegant charts.",
  "feature5Title": "Fully Customizable",
  "feature5Desc": "Tailor your financial assistant to your lifestyle. Create your own categories, set your quick entry amounts, and celebrate your achievements with unique badges.",
  "aboutHeroDesc": "Pretio isn't just an ordinary budget tracker; it's a personal life philosophy that gives you back control over your time, money, and emotions. Amidst the frenzy of consumerism, it is designed to remind you of your own willpower and illuminate the path to your dreams.",
  "aboutSection1Title": "Meaning of the Name",
  "aboutSection1Desc": "Pretio derives its roots from the Latin word \"pretium\", meaning \"value\", \"worth\", and \"price\". Everything we buy in life comes not just at a financial cost, but at a true price paid with our time and emotions. Pretio exists to show you this true value.",
  "aboutSection2Title": "Its Simplicity",
  "aboutSection2Desc": "It doesn't overwhelm you with complex financial tables, confusing menus, and exhausting charts. With its easy-on-the-eyes, minimalist design, it turns financial tracking from a source of stress into a peaceful daily routine.",
  "aboutSection3Title": "Its Awareness",
  "aboutSection3Desc": "It shows you not just what you spend, but why you spend it. Illuminating your consumption psychology, it helps you understand whether the item you bought is a genuine need or a momentary whim.",
  "aboutSection4Title": "Its Practicality",
  "aboutSection4Desc": "It perfectly keeps up with the pace of daily life. You can log expenses in seconds without filling out long and tedious forms, update your budget with a single touch, and summarize your financial status at a glance.",
  "aboutSection5Title": "Its Customizability",
  "aboutSection5Desc": "Everyone's lifestyle and financial journey is unique to them. You can fully tailor Pretio to your own habits by creating your own spending categories, setting personalized goals, and adjusting your quick entry amounts.",
  "aboutFooterNote": "This app was brought to life by an independent group of developers to help you protect your own willpower against the frenzy of consumerism.",
